name: Missing Tax and Shipping measurement
description: It is good to measure tax and shipping in order to have complete view on ecommerce dimensions. This test is evaluating data from last week to detect any tax or shipping in the transactions.

blocks.description: Test checks if the sum of taxes across all transactions is not zero, if it is, it shows message.
Test checks if the sum of shipping across all transactions is not zero, if it is, it shows message.
